01:26:58.030 --> 01:27:01.275
I now understand that we have the

01:27:01.337 --> 01:27:04.761
opportunity for a wonderful song that my

01:27:04.801 --> 01:27:08.509
wife has written for this occasion.

01:27:09.050 --> 01:27:10.271
Please listen and enjoy.

01:27:39.634 --> 01:27:44.435
Children of Israel, hear my voice.

01:27:46.396 --> 01:27:48.417
I called you by name.

01:27:49.537 --> 01:27:51.719
I gave you a choice,

01:27:51.798 --> 01:27:54.581
a plan to lift you on wings.

01:27:55.381 --> 01:28:02.484
So high to walk in my light beneath

01:28:02.684 --> 01:28:03.925
endless sky.

01:28:07.213 --> 01:28:12.404
I gave you guidance, loving and true.

01:28:13.305 --> 01:28:17.434
A father's heart reaching out to you.

01:28:22.194 --> 01:28:27.737
answered my plea you turned from the truth

01:28:27.817 --> 01:28:37.680
and chose to be free free to stray

01:28:37.819 --> 01:28:38.860
and that you are

01:28:51.820 --> 01:28:58.444
my people why do you roam i inscribed

01:28:58.484 --> 01:29:03.105
your name but you left the home i

01:29:03.166 --> 01:29:08.609
sent my son the path to walk but

01:29:08.668 --> 01:29:14.150
you walked away rejected us both a family

01:29:14.190 --> 01:29:18.132
torn love unreturned one last chance one

01:29:18.233 --> 01:29:18.432
last

01:29:24.984 --> 01:29:27.686
The path less traveled yet It shows the

01:29:27.726 --> 01:29:30.529
way our voice grows cold In the night's

01:29:30.569 --> 01:29:40.917
sway our lament Our unanswered call Stand

01:29:40.979 --> 01:29:44.320
before Yahowah My name is above all none

01:29:44.341 --> 01:29:48.604
beside me Yet you chase whispers that only

01:29:48.664 --> 01:29:49.145
fall

01:29:51.804 --> 01:29:54.105
I gave you a covenant,

01:29:54.645 --> 01:30:00.030
a golden word But voices of falsehood

01:30:00.451 --> 01:30:05.715
drowned what you heard Still hope remains

01:30:05.755 --> 01:30:11.399
for hearts that break For those who turn

01:30:11.439 --> 01:30:14.643
for love's own sake Return to you

01:30:36.564 --> 01:30:39.488
Like errant sheep without pasture,

01:30:39.628 --> 01:30:42.692
I inscribed your name, ha-Mayim, your home.

01:30:43.171 --> 01:30:45.494
I sent my son, God,

01:30:45.614 --> 01:30:47.516
as the path to see,

01:30:47.577 --> 01:30:53.684
but you walked away, rejected me.

01:30:53.743 --> 01:30:55.786
A family torn asunder,

01:30:55.865 --> 01:30:58.588
a love unrequited in my open arms.

01:31:02.136 --> 01:31:04.976
Two men standing in the standing place The

01:31:05.037 --> 01:31:09.078
sign of Zion marks the ground In the

01:31:09.158 --> 01:31:12.720
place where I put my name

01:31:31.865 --> 01:31:33.806
Children of Yisrael,

01:31:34.067 --> 01:31:39.088
I know this is true No greater love

01:31:39.128 --> 01:31:44.631
than I have for you Though broken hearts

01:31:44.711 --> 01:31:51.672
and paths astray I'll wait for you to

01:31:51.733 --> 01:31:53.073
come home

